title: Travels
text:
I love to travel and try to do it every chance I get. I’m currently trying to visit every unit in the National Park Service system. So far I have visited 45 out of the 432 units. These images show many of the places I have traveled.
The order is as followed:
Isle Royale NP 2024
Badlands NP 2016
Glacier NP 2023 (Images 3 -4)
Mount Rushmore 2024
Boulder CO 2022
Crater Lake NP 2021
Blue Mountains, Australia 2022 (Images 8-10)
The Great Barrier Reef 2022
Devil’s Tower National Monument
Zion NP 2018
Arches NP 2018
Redwood NP 2021
San Francisco 2019
Oregon Coast 2021

title: Walker Fryar
text:
Hello, my name is Walker Fryar, and I’m a student at Colorado State University. I’m currently working towards a Professional Science Master’s in Ecosystem Science and Sustainability with a focus in Sustainable Food Systems. With my degree, I am planning on going into agricultural consulting to help farmers and ranchers implement more sustainable practices.
Feel free to explore this website to learn more about me and my experiences!
